"title": "8746: false Christs",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8746: false christs",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Mistaken and deceptive people claiming to be Jesus Christ. Jesus Christ warns his followers to be on their guard against the appearance of such people.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ warns that false Christs will appear</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:5\">MAT 24:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:6\">MRK 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:8\">LUK 21:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:23\">MAT 24:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:21\">MRK 13:21</a></p>\n<h2>False Christs will perform signs and miracles in order to deceive</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">MRK 13:22</a></p>\n<h2>False Christs can be recognised because the return of Jesus Christ will be obvious to everyone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:27-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:27–24:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:24-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:24–13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:25-Luke21:28\">LUK 21:25–21:28</a> <em>The personal return of the Lord Jesus Christ is not described in terms of an appearance to a select group, but to the whole world. The attempt of anyone to convince others that he is Christ therefore is a sure sign of deception.</em></p>",
